metadata.name: Impression N.01 #16
metadata.description:
Combinations of coded masks (see https://sites.google.com/view/tidally-disrupted-star/ ) and guided randomly generated backgrounds.
Right click in the image and 'save as’ will allow to save the image.

Some combinations of colors, coded mask aperture and orientation are rarer than others.
Token rarity will be given at the end of the process.

Follow me on Twitter: @TidallyD
More informations on my Coded Mask Project : https://sites.google.com/view/tidally-disrupted-star/

metadata.name: Timing #355
metadata.description:
Time.. 
While one thing happens one time, another happens several times.

----------------------------------------------------------------
  Keys control:
    r: toggle rotation
    i: increment rotation speed
    d: decrement rotation speed
    p: toggle show points
    s: save current size image to .png
    x + 2/4/8: save 2x/4x/8x size image to .png
    1-9 + g: save 1-9 sec animation to .gif (depends on the machine resources)

  URL parameters:
    fps=<value>: frame rate
    r=true: rotation ON
    p=false: do not show points 

---------------------------------------------------------------
